Class PositionSortingStrategy<MenuItem>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drombler.acp.core.action.PositionSortingStrategy<MenuItem>

    MenuItem - the GUI toolkit specific type for menu items

    public class PositionSortingStrategy<MenuItem>
extends Object
implements MenuItemSortingStrategy<MenuItem,PositionableMenuItemAdapterFactory<MenuItem>>
    The default position-based sorting strategy for declaratively registered menus and menu items. This sorting strategy will add separators between menu items in different thousand steps.
